 Regarding "Crossing the Culture Line" (by Lydia Chavez, Aug. 28): Activists 
Karen Bass and Bong Hwan Kim are among the best and the brightest in a new 
alliance of community coalition builders.I am pleased that they are finally 
receiving the recognition they so richly deserve. 
