<P>
 The Thing Called Love (Cinemax Tuesday at 10:30 a.m.) has not yet been 
released theatrically. It is Peter Bogdanovich's 1993 film with Samantha 
Mathis, who dreams of Nashville stardom, and is most notable for one of River 
Phoenix's last performances.He is impressive as another singer, the kind who 
keeps his emotions to himself. 
