<P>
PALM LATITUDES: VERBATIM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Cordiality, Hollywood-style: 
</P>
<P>
 Castle Rock Entertainment corially invites you and a guest to the all media 
screening of The Shawshank Redemption. . .Please RSVP by September 19th.Theatre 
is overbooked to ensure capacity and we strongly recommend you ARRIVE EARLY. At 
the theatre, seating is on a first come, first served bases. Passes DO NOT 
guarantee seating. You must present this ticket for admittance into the 
theatre. No one will be admitted after the screening begins. 
</P>
<P>
 All things considered, we'd rather just pay our seven bucks. 
</P>
