<P>
GEORGE AND BARBARA BUSH HEAD TO GUATEMALA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Former President George Bush and his wife, Barbara, will visit Guatemala today 
on a relief mission sponsored by the private U.S. aid agency AmeriCares. 
</P>
<P>
 AmeriCares spokesman Dwain Schenck said the Bushes will spend the day in 
