<DOCID> 084781 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 2, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Opinion; Part M; Page 1; Column 1; Opinion Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
